      <Feature>extended the ScrapeDialog with the ability to download torrents from an url and display them</Feature>
      <Feature>SSL availability &amp; status is shown in the Az plugin config</Feature>
      <Change>New Logo and Splash Screen</Change>
      <Change>Connection Dialog can now save unlimited profiles</Change>
      <Change>Message Popup Shell was changed to behave like the Az one, especially not blocking AzSMRC when many messages are coming in</Change>
